00643866528a3208920c742a060ddb7d63df4152.query:
SELECT
                url,
                title,
                tags,
                via,
                notes,
                found_at,
                read_at,
                published_at,
                from_filename,
                image,
                src,
                meta,
                last_fetched,
                last_processed,
                http_headers
            FROM "links" WHERE "url" = ?

525d145902c26750a6912913727bc4a3b0c4155a.query:
INSERT INTO "links" (
                title,
                tags,
                via,
                notes,
                found_at,
                read_at,
                from_filename,
                url,
                image,
                src,
                meta,
                last_fetched,
                last_processed,
                http_headers
            ) VALUES (
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?,
                ?
            ) ON CONFLICT (url) DO UPDATE
                SET title=excluded.title,
                    tags=excluded.tags,
                    via=excluded.via,
                    notes=excluded.notes,
                    found_at=excluded.found_at,
                    read_at=excluded.read_at,
                    from_filename=excluded.from_filename,
                    image=excluded.image,
                    src=excluded.src,
                    meta=excluded.meta,
                    last_fetched=excluded.last_fetched,
                    last_processed=excluded.last_processed,
                    http_headers=excluded.http_headers

d6bae5ba568989f7f7aa00f763076263001fe77a.query:
SELECT
                    url,
                    title,
                    tags,
                    via,
                    notes,
                    found_at,
                    read_at,
                    published_at,
                    from_filename,
                    image,
                    NULL as "src?: Vec<u8>", -- explicitly DO NOT FETCH the source data
                    meta,
                    last_fetched,
                    last_processed,
                    http_headers
                FROM "links"
